    OpenStack Neutron v2.0 Load Balancer as a service (LBaaS) bindings. See OpenStack Network API v2.0 Reference for description of the fields: Implemented fields are as follows: id uuid-str tenant_id uuid-str type String delay Integer timeout Integer max_retries Integer http_method String url_path String expected_codes String admin_state_up Boolean status String http://docs.openstack.org/api/openstack-network/2.0/openstack-network.pdf
